'''潘傑瓦伊槍擊案（又称：坎大哈大屠杀）'''是指2012年3月11日发生于[[阿富汗|阿富汗]][[坎大哈省|坎大哈省]]{{Internal link helper/en|潘傑瓦伊|Panjwayi District}}的屠殺事件<ref>Shah, Taimoor, "Days Of Horror And Grief: Reporting The Panjwai Massacre", ''[[New_York_Times|New York Times]]'', 9 November 2012</ref>，共造成阿富汗平民十六名死亡、五名受傷，包括婦女和兒童。其中有十一名死者来自同一个家庭，部分尸体被焚尸。駐扎當地美軍基地的陸軍上士'''羅伯特·貝爾斯'''（Robert Bales，1973年生于[[俄亥俄州|俄亥俄州]]）被指控是兇手<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.sina.com.hk/news/12/1/1/2609769/1.html|title=殺阿富汗平民美軍身分曝光|date=2012-03-17|publisher=新浪網|accessdate=}}{{dead link|date=2018年3月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>，他在事后被拘留并承认罪行。2013年8月23日，罗伯特·贝尔斯被美国军事法院判处[[终身监禁|终身监禁]]且不得[[假释|假释]]<ref name="GetsLife">{{cite news|title=Soldier Gets Life Without Parole in Deaths of Afghan Civilians|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/08/24/us/soldier-gets-life-without-parole-in-deaths-of-afghan-civilians.html?emc=edit_na_20130823&_r=0|publisher=''[[New_York_Times|New York Times]]''|accessdate=August 23, 2013|archive-date=2019-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190427160130/https://www.nytimes.com/2013/08/24/us/soldier-gets-life-without-parole-in-deaths-of-afghan-civilians.html?emc=edit_na_20130823&_r=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[駐阿富汗國際維和部隊|驻阿富汗国际维和部队]](ISAF)为此次事件中所造成的遇难平民向阿富汗社会致歉，阿富汗当局谴责这一行为是“蓄意谋杀”。[[国民议会_(阿富汗)|阿富汗国民议会]]通过了一项决议，要求在阿富汗举行{{Internal link helper/en|公开审判|Public trial}}，但当时的[[美国国防部长|美国国防部长]][[莱昂·帕内塔|莱昂·帕内塔]]称，这名士兵将被送回国并受到{{Internal link helper/en|美国军事法|Uniform Code of Military Justice}}审判。羅伯特·貝爾斯于2013年6月5日对其指控的16项[[謀殺|谋杀]]罪名表示认罪，以换取控方取消对他的[[死刑|死刑]]诉求。在认罪时，他说他并不知道他为什么会犯下这些谋杀罪。

美国当局的最后定论是，潘杰瓦伊枪击案完全是由罗伯特·贝尔斯一人所犯下。2012年3月15日，由阿富汗国民议会的几名成员组成的阿富汗议会调查小组推测指出，多达20名美国士兵参与了这次屠杀，但该小组后来表示，他们其实也无法证实有多名士兵参与屠杀的说法。

== 背景 ==

==== 对阿富汗南部的“增兵” ====
{{see also|阿富汗戰爭 (2001年)}}
[[File:Patrolling_the_Panjwayi_district_near_Kandahar_-b.jpg|thumb]]
潘杰瓦伊县是塔利班运动的发源地，且历来也是[[塔利班|塔利班]]的大本营。<ref name=csm>{{cite news |title=Taliban fire on Afghan president's brothers at shooting memorial service |url=http://www.csmonitor.com/World/Latest-News-Wires/2012/0313/Taliban-fire-on-Afghan-president-s-brothers-at-shooting-memorial-service |newspaper=[[The_Christian_Science_Monitor|The Christian Science Monitor]] |agency=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]] |date=13 March 2012 |access-date=13 March 2012 |archive-date=2012-03-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120314124717/http://www.csmonitor.com/World/Latest-News-Wires/2012/0313/Taliban-fire-on-Afghan-president-s-brothers-at-shooting-memorial-service |dead-url=no }}</ref>由于美军与塔利班在这个地区时长发生激烈冲突，潘杰瓦伊地区也是美国在2010年增兵应对的重点地区，[[美国空军|美国空军]]对此地区的空袭打击增加了2倍，<ref>{{Cite web|title=What the numbers say about progress in Afghanistan|url=https://politicalticker.blogs.cnn.com/2010/10/15/what-the-numbers-say-about-progress-in-afghanistan/|access-date=2021-06-11|language=en|archive-date=2021-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211109211348/https://politicalticker.blogs.cnn.com/2010/10/15/what-the-numbers-say-about-progress-in-afghanistan/|dead-url=no}}</ref>更是在夜间也不断对该地区的村庄或建筑进行空袭打击<ref>{{cite news |title=Study: NATO night raids cause Afghan backlash |url=http://www.defensenews.com/article/20110919/DEFSECT04/109190312/Study-NATO-night-raids-cause-Afghan-backlash |agency=[[Agence_France-Presse|Agence France-Presse]] |newspaper=[[Defense_News|Defense News]] |date=19 September 2011 |access-date=22 March 2012 |archive-date=2012-07-28 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20120728195345/http://www.defensenews.com/article/20110919/DEFSECT04/109190312/Study-NATO-night-raids-cause-Afghan-backlash |dead-url=yes }}</ref> ，空袭造成了大量当地叛乱分子伤亡。<ref name="schmitt">{{cite news |author=Eric Schmitt |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2010/12/27/world/asia/27policy.html?_r=2&ref=world |title=Taliban Fighters Appear Blunted in Afghanistan |work=The New York Times |access-date=31 January 2011 |location=Washington |date=26 December 2010 |archive-date=2021-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308234028/https://www.nytimes.com/2010/12/27/world/asia/27policy.html?_r=2 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 同时，美国特种部队在阿富汗全境的行动也增加了六倍以上。<ref name="miller">{{cite news |url=http://www.latimes.com/news/nationworld/world/la-fg-afghan-intel20-2009sep20,0,1183243.story?page=2 |title=CIA expanding presence in Afghanistan |work=Los Angeles Times |access-date=9 February 2010 |first=Greg |last=Miller |date=20 September 2009 |archive-date=2009-09-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090926070809/http://www.latimes.com/news/nationworld/world/la-fg-afghan-intel20-2009sep20,0,1183243.story?page=2 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

潘杰瓦伊县以及邻近的扎里县、阿尔甘达布县、[[坎大哈县|坎大哈县]]在阿富汗都属于常年发生激战的地区。平民与美军之间的冲突因美军大规模摧毁村庄<ref>{{cite news |title=NATO Is Razing Booby-Trapped Afghan Homes |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2010/11/17/world/asia/17afghan.html |newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |date=16 November 2010 |access-date=18 March 2012 |first1=Taimoor |last1=Shah |first2=Rod |last2=Nordland |archive-date=2018-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181124163051/https://www.nytimes.com/2010/11/17/world/asia/17afghan.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>、逮捕村民<ref name="porter">Porter, Gareth: [https://wayback.archive-it.org/all/20110713152532/http://atimes.com/atimes/South_Asia/LL21Df02.html Kandahar gains come with "brutal" tactics]. ''[[Asia_Times|Asia Times]]'', 21 December 2010.</ref>、不守纪士兵杀害无辜村民<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.spiegel.de/international/world/0,1518,754554,00.html |title=Murder in Afghanistan: SPIEGEL TV's 'Kill Team' Documentary |work=[[Spiegel_Online|Spiegel Online]] |date=4 January 2011 |accessdate=2021-06-12 |archive-date=2018-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181224225925/http://www.spiegel.de/international/world/0,1518,754554,00.html%20 |dead-url=no }}</ref>以及[[簡易爆炸裝置|简易爆炸装置]]造成大量伤亡而进一步加剧<ref name="norland">Norland, Rod and Taimoor Shah: [https://www.nytimes.com/2010/11/17/world/asia/17afghan.html NATO is Razing Booby-Trapped Afghan Homes] {{Wayback|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2010/11/17/world/asia/17afghan.html |date=20181124163051 }}. ''[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]'', 16 November 2010.</ref>。2011年，一个因美国增兵和军事打击活动加剧而流离失所的家庭重返潘杰瓦伊县，由于他们受到美国政府、军队和阿富汗政府的鼓励，他们选择在不会被塔利班袭击的美国军事基地附近定居，因为他们认为那里是一个比较安全的居住地。<ref>{{cite news |title=Afghan Massacre: After Losing Homes in NATO Attacks, Victims Moved Near U.S. Base Hoping for Safety |url=http://www.democracynow.org/2012/3/14/after_afghan_massacre_grievers_left_to |work=[[Democracy_Now!|Democracy Now!]] |date=14 March 2012 |access-date=15 March 2012 |archive-date=2019-05-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190519041938/https://www.democracynow.org/2012/3/14/after_afghan_massacre_grievers_left_to |dead-url=no }}</ref>

在潘杰瓦伊枪击案事件发生前的三个星期，阿富汗和美国的关系就因{{Internal link helper/en|巴格拉姆空军基地焚烧古兰经事件|2012 Afghanistan Quran burning protests}}而变得紧张。在枪击案发生的几个月前，[[美国海军陆战队|美国海军陆战队员]]还被拍到在死去的塔利班战士身上{{Internal link helper/en|撒尿的视频|Video of U.S. Marines urinating on Taliban fighters}}。

==== 对刘易斯-麦科德联合基地的指控 ====
潘杰瓦伊枪击案枪手罗伯特·贝尔斯来自[[路易斯–麥克喬德聯合基地|路易斯–麥克喬德聯合基地]](JBLM)。该基地的主要医疗设施{{Internal link helper/en|马迪根陆军医疗中心|Madigan Army Medical Center}}(Madigan Army medical Center)因将患有[[創傷後壓力症候群|PTSD]]心理疾病的士兵诊断为较轻状态而受到调查。该基地周围的军事支助团体称，基地指挥官在派遣返国士兵的下一次部署之前，没有给予他们足够的恢复时间，而且该基地还存在医疗人员不足的情况，而返国士兵的人数又较多，这些士兵又皆在战场上或多或少的有身体和心理上的创伤。<ref name="finn">{{cite news|title=Afghan shootings refocus attention at Fort Lewis-McChord base|author=Finn, Peter|last2=Leonnig|first2=Carol D.|author-link2=Carol D. Leonnig|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/national-security/afghan-shootings-refocus-attention-on-fort-lewis-mcchord/2012/03/13/gIQApTNYAS_story.html|newspaper=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]]|date=14 March 2012|page=16|access-date=15 March 2012|archive-date=2019-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190611124250/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/national-security/afghan-shootings-refocus-attention-on-fort-lewis-mcchord/2012/03/13/gIQApTNYAS_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>Yardley, William, Serge F. Kovaleski and James Dao, "Home Base of Accused Soldier Has Faced Scrutiny", ''[[New_York_Times|New York Times]]'', 14 March 2012.</ref>

有许多的战争暴行和罪行都与该基地的士兵有联系。2010年，梅万德谋杀案就涉及JBLM的士兵，<ref name="clues">{{cite news|last1=Whitlock|first1=Craig|first2=Carol D.|last2=Leonnig|author-link2=Carol D. Leonnig|title=Seeking Clues in Afghan Killings|newspaper=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]]|date=13 March 2012|page=1}}</ref>而在美国[[盐湖城|盐湖城]]一名刚刚因“擅离职守”而从该基地退伍的士兵则枪杀了一名警察。<ref>Murphy, Kim, "Soldier Held in Killings Is From A Troubled Base", ''[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]'', 13 March 2012, p. 1.</ref> 2011年4月，一名JBLM士兵杀死了他的妻子和5岁的儿子，然后开枪自尽。<ref name=finn/> 2012年1月，一名JBLM士兵则谋杀了一名[[雷尼尔山国家公园|雷尼尔山国家公园]]的护林员。<ref name="clues" /> 在另外两起独立案件中，涉及的JBLM士兵被控对他们的孩子使用[[水刑|水刑]]。<ref name="finn" />

路易斯–麥克喬德聯合基地附近一个退伍军人资源中心的执行主任豪尔赫·冈萨雷斯说，潘杰瓦伊枪击案是证明基地功能失序的重要证据，他在一份声明中称：“这不是一个不守纪士兵的问题，这是基地领导层严重领导失误的问题，JBLM完全就是一个流氓基地。”<ref name="katu">{{cite web|title=Lewis-McChord soldier accused in killings of Afghan civilians|url=http://www.katu.com/news/national/Report-Soldier-accused-in-Afghan-killings-from-Lewis-McChord-142249635.html|date=11 March 2012|publisher=[[KATU|KATU]]|access-date=2021-06-12|archive-date=2012-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120315043807/http://www.katu.com/news/national/Report-Soldier-accused-in-Afghan-killings-from-Lewis-McChord-142249635.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 基地官员对此声明作出回应，称其士兵犯下的罪行是完全孤立的事件，“并不能代表基地所有服役人员的工作态度和奉献精神”。<ref>{{cite news|title=Lt. Colonel Charged in Flurry of Threats|first=Jonathan|last=Martin|url=http://seattletimes.nwsource.com/html/localnews/2017741698_ltcol14m.html?syndication=rss|newspaper=[[The_Seattle_Times|The Seattle Times]]|date=13 March 2012|access-date=15 March 2012}}</ref>美国退休陆军少将、陆军战争学院前校长{{Internal link helper/en|罗伯特·H·斯卡尔斯|Robert H. Scales}}(Robert H. Scales)认为，枪击事件的主要原因是过去十年间在伊拉克、阿富汗和其他地方过渡投入步兵人员在近距离战斗中。<ref>{{cite news|title=Consumed by wars without end|first=Robert H.|last=Scales|author-link=Robert H. Scales|url=http://www.sltrib.com/sltrib/opinion/53717260-82/combat-army-infantry-soldiers.html.csp|newspaper=[[The_Salt_Lake_Tribune|The Salt Lake Tribune]]|date=14 March 2012|access-date=15 March 2012|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303222639/http://www.sltrib.com/sltrib/opinion/53717260-82/combat-army-infantry-soldiers.html.csp|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==== 3月8日路边炸弹事件 ====
3月8日，位于贝兰拜营地东约500米的摩库亚村的村民表示，一枚路边炸弹在他们附近爆炸，摧毁了一辆装甲车，并造成几名美国士兵受伤。<ref name=retaliation/> 他们说，美军士兵随后让许多男性村民站在墙边，威胁说“至少要处决20名当地村民，以为此次事件受伤的战友报仇”，并威胁补充“你和你们的孩子将为此付出代价”。<ref name=retaliation/>一位摩库亚村村民对[[美联社|美联社]]表示，“当时他们看起来就像真的要开枪打我们，我感到非常害怕。”<ref name=retaliation/> [[五角大楼|五角大楼]]的美国官员宣称，村民根本就“没有证据”能证明男性村民靠墙站成一排并受到威胁的说法。<ref name="nbcpent">{{cite web|url=http://worldnews.msnbc.msn.com/_news/2012/03/21/10795362-pentagon-no-evidence-afghan-massacre-was-a-retaliation |title=Pentagon: No evidence Afghan massacre was a retaliation |publisher=Worldnews.msnbc.msn.com |access-date=2012-04-22 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120504041408/http://worldnews.msnbc.msn.com/_news/2012/03/21/10795362-pentagon-no-evidence-afghan-massacre-was-a-retaliation |archive-date= 4 May 2012 }}</ref> 美国官员拒绝证实或否认3月8日美国士兵在村庄外遇袭受伤。<ref name=retaliation />

罗伯特·贝尔斯的律师{{Internal link helper/en|约翰·亨利·布朗|John Henry Browne}}(John Henry Browne)后来说，贝尔斯当时听到路边炸弹这个消息很是气愤，因为他的一名战友在3月9日的一次爆炸中失去了一条腿。<ref name=retaliation/> 但目前还不清楚布朗所说的爆炸是否与村民们描述的爆炸是不是一件事。<ref name=retaliation>{{cite news |title=Villagers: Afghan slayings were act of retaliation |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/feedarticle/10154872 |agency=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]] |newspaper=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |date=21 March 2012 |access-date=22 March 2012 |location=London}}</ref>

